text: The fruit with the most protein is guava. The fruit with the least protein is grapes. The fruit with the most calcium is oranges. The fruit with the least calcium is pineapple. The fruit with the most potassium is bananas. The fruit with the least potassium is blueberries. The fruit with the most fiber is raspberries. The fruit with the least fiber is watermelon.
